Texts.DescBR: Ganha +1 PM enquanto houver uma invocação adversária diante dela.
Texts.DescEN: Gains +1 MP as long as an enemy Minion is in front of her.
Texts.DescES: Gana +1 PM mientras haya una invocación enemiga delante de ella.
Texts.DescFR: Gagne +1 PM tant qu’une invocation adverse est devant elle.
Texts.DescRU: Получает +1 ОП, пока перед ней находится существо противника.
